  "detailed_description": "<h1>OUR NEW GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is SokoChess White?</h2>SokoChess White is a unique game in which you must use your wits to navigate each level, moving and pushing pieces on the chessboard until they reach their destination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Push your own pieces</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.poster.avif?t=1757579636\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.webm?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/2c52880c69f372b0727c5f7a13463b39.mp4?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The goal of each level is to get all the white pieces to their destination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond Chess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.poster.avif?t=1757579636\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.webm?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/c8f425849ac0fa6f1c272e8912d8dd34.mp4?t=1757579636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Overcome many unique obstacles before unseen in Chess!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185860/extras/f07a4af4500ac67319d6dfaa42a53ebc.avif?t=1757579636\" width=620 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 70 handcrafted levels<br></li><li> Infinite undos<br></li><li> Puzzle elements you won't see in Chess<br></li><li> Unique and chill gameplay combining Chess and Sokoban<br></li><li> Don't like a level you are playing? Skip it!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Chess like never before!</h2>",
